		.col.product-description
			h5 MODBUS/BACNET INTEGRATION
			p.modbus
				|A BACnet building automation system may include HVAC, 
				|lighting, and life safety subsystems. The EVO/ECM-Modbus 
				|RTU fan system can now be integrated to a BACnet building  
				|automation network through Modbus to BACnet gateways to 
				|operate in response to other subsystems. The gateway directs 
				|the data flow back and forth between BACnet’s subsystems 
				|and the Modbus network.
				br
				br
				|The EVO/ECM-BACnet-Modebus library provides
				|the mapping files for the Control Solutions 
				|B1-10x Babel Buster SPX gateway to translate 
				|between the EVO/ECM-Modbus RTU registers and the BACnet objects.
				|See the intgration section in the Application Guide for detail.
